    "body": "Phase 3 completed\r\n- PRsuggestion will respond with codebase as the context, means more meaningful response.\r\n- ChromaDB vector store integration with APIs to fetch data and delete collections.\r\n- Flow is, when the `/pr-analyze` API is called, it will populate the vector store with files changed in the PR, and call the AI with the prompt `Given the following context from the codebase and this PR diff <pr_diff>, summarize and suggest improvements.` with the exact codebase for these changed files as the context for the AI to provide meaningful response. \r\n- Way too many changes on finding the free embedding model :)",
